  "remarks": "Pursuant to paragraphs 8(d) of Security Council resolution 1718 (2006) and 12 of Security Council resolution 2270 (2016) as economic resources of designated entities. DPRK cargo vessel M/V HAP JANG GANG 6 is owned by Hapjanggang Shipping Corp and is believed to have been involved in illicit transfers of prohibited DPRK goods. Listed as asset of Hapjanggang Shipping Corp, (OFSI ID: 13629, UN Reference Number: UN Ref KPe.058)",
